{"tid":1817904,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"大龍生三太 樊亦敏後生靚到。。","createTime":"2020-01-09T12:44:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-12T10:24:15.000Z","uid":222907,"like":547,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":78,"replies":[{"pid":"83d897b1021ce56b66baaa0a3add14c95920bfe2","tid":1817904,"uid":222907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T12:44:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KondvvL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKondvvL.jpg&h=550eb521&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m3ZzeXr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm3ZzeXr.jpg&h=0edac8e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家d是非精真係企埋一邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b42839b98f69cca918d9bdc47aa965754b5cb728","tid":1817904,"uid":198590,"like":71,"dislike":4,"score":67,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T12:45:00.000Z","msg":"會員 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#222907 - 金大喜</span></strong> 極有可能係<span style=\"color: gold;\">五毛, 分化撚, mon-post狗或網軍</span><br />\n請大家保持批判性思考，善用不推文回覆，該會員以往言論：<br />\n<br />\n<code>APM有人成功劏狗? - #23</code><br />\n<blockquote>企圖謀殺<br />\n衰撚硬<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fagree.gif&h=7a38d91f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1651421/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=23\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1651421/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=23</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>勇武最叻問藍絲媽咪拎零用錢買飯食 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>阿媽話 : 無啊，你打得咁叻，有本事自已搵啊<br />\n<br />\n勇武憤怒，不停敲打家中度門<br />\n<br />\n阿媽問 : 你想拆屋呀?<br />\n<br />\n其後阿媽就範並比4條野個勇武並道 : 怕左你啦，唔好搞野呀!<br />\n<br />\n勇武沾沾自喜心想 : 拳頭就是一切<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fslick.gif&h=00e43c9f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1634582/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1634582/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>原來 救護 消防 海關都係毅進仔 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>毅進文憑的資歷獲政府接納為符合超過30個以中學文憑試5科(包括中國語文和英國語文科)第2級成績為入職學歷的公務員職位的學歷要求，這些職位包括救護員、三級康樂助理員、助理外勤統計主任、二級懲教助理、海關關員、消防員、警員、郵務員、社會保障助理員、二級稅務督察及福利工作員等。而成功修畢註 1延伸數學選修科的學員獲頒發的毅進文憑，亦獲政府接納為符合以中學文憑試5科(包括中國語文、英國語文和數學科)第2級成績為入職學歷的公務員職位的學歷要求，這些職位為助理文書主任、助理稅務主任、助理貿易管制主任、二級地政督察及二級物料供應員。</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1328431/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1328431/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>你地係想警察完全唔介入遊行？ - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>感覺近幾次遊行最終目的都係向警察發洩<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fdead.gif&h=caf0bd2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好期待一次遊行係完全無警察，睇示威者做得出d乜。</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1318028/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1318028/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>支持舉報南亞仔 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>阿叔打人就個個要告刑事<br />\n咁南亞仔同粉紅背心男呢？？<br />\n公平d啦<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fdonno.gif&h=765fac39&s={SIZE}\" />打人就係打人</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1308417/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1308417/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n意見及舉報： <a href=\"http://lih.kg/1707551\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/1707551</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/kBN5bas.jpg\" />"},{"pid":"9d9ede59916e8a5be8e9c9ca6f61c241cc727d4f","tid":1817904,"uid":222907,"li