職位的學歷要求，這些職位包括救護員、三級康樂助理員、助理外勤統計主任、二級懲教助理、海關關員、消防員、警員、郵務員、社會保障助理員、二級稅務督察及福利工作員等。而成功修畢註 1延伸數學選修科的學員獲頒發的毅進文憑，亦獲政府接納為符合以中學文憑試5科(包括中國語文、英國語文和數學科)第2級成績為入職學歷的公務員職位的學歷要求，這些職位為助理文書主任、助理稅務主任、助理貿易管制主任、二級地政督察及二級物料供應員。</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1328431/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1328431/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>你地係想警察完全唔介入遊行？ - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>感覺近幾次遊行最終目的都係向警察發洩<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fdead.gif&h=caf0bd2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好期待一次遊行係完全無警察，睇示威者做得出d乜。</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1318028/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1318028/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>支持舉報南亞仔 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>阿叔打人就個個要告刑事<br />\n咁南亞仔同粉紅背心男呢？？<br />\n公平d啦<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fdonno.gif&h=765fac39&s={SIZE}\" />打人就係打人</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1308417/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1308417/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n意見及舉報： <a href=\"http://lih.kg/1707551\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/1707551</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/kBN5bas.jpg\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T06:34:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"810f269337cb1c63976385b080f818b838e35fb3","tid":1817904,"uid":277137,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T06:47:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9bd46798d12871392bbe57761739a3c88b7e2689","tid":1817904,"uid":23897,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score"