"uid":60655,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T05:30:06.000Z","msg":"以前d妹仔 都完勝依家班一姐"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T07:45:59.000Z","msg":"真 <br />\n伍慧珊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c768828d6637e9208f9e0b81dd6bd6bb9c1ef2cb","tid":1817904,"uid":48222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T07:48:30.000Z","msg":"依家都好靚"},{"pid":"8a08438bd4524f26b448c2fb09eaf584001aac9e","tid":1817904,"uid":256019,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T07:56:09.000Z","msg":"俠義救風塵 樊亦敏 壹周刊 1228期 豪語錄<br />\n<br />\n我是，慣曾為旅偏憐客，自己貪杯惜醉人。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;元曲‧關漢卿《救風塵》<br />\n<br />\n藝人通常講義氣，係，講之嘛，做的很少，樊亦敏卻做得到。劉家輝中風癱瘓，先是妻兒不顧，繼而助手賬目不清，樊亦敏攬上身，什麼清官難審家庭事、當街攔截遞上法庭傳票，她都幹了。劉師傅練武之人，師門廣大，到頭來可靠的是最上鏡港姐。<br />\n<br />\n咁都未算怪，怪在，樊亦敏從不是圈中強勢者，正如上述曲文，自己孑然一身卻同情孤客，自己愛杯中物卻勸人少飲&mdash;&mdash;比喻而已，樊亦敏無酗酒習慣，其實想問的是&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n她倒坦白：「直接吧，有錢人幫人係做善事，窮人去幫人就另有所圖。大家覺得我怪，應該是將我定義為窮人。」樊亦敏愈笑愈豪邁：「但俗語不是『仗義每多屠狗輩』嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n這句畫龍點睛了，因為俗語的下聯是「自古俠女出風塵」，樊女俠巾幗不讓鬚眉，而且真帶點風塵味。她是傳奇富豪羅兆輝首位圈中紅顏知己，公認最有情有義。交情本不深的劉家輝固然要救，何況羅兆輝潦倒大陸身亡，她原來也曾盡力至今耿耿於懷。義氣，係一貫敢（咁）做嘅。"},{"pid":"f573421c8c007dcdb5c5249add3dc30a1a43dc7d","tid":1817904,"uid":75556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T07:57:16.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"22a193e83897ba7fafbd2ee4d7e680f8ccd56b89","tid":1817904,"uid":137699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T08:23:34.000Z","msg":"善用不推文回覆"},{"pid":"61fa3b3bdb8fc843c86c323596498fea16312dd4","tid":1817904,"uid":236669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T08:49:06.000Z","msg":"1. 叫立會議員set 運動agenda （非大台）<br />\n2. 盡量功能組別搶票 （ 得返ard 2 個月）<br />\n3. 警暴影片/証據留底， Send 去聯合國存檔<br />\n4. 繼續經濟攬炒 （防止中科技股回港集資）<br />\n5. 每人行多一步，諗下自己做到咩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔想運動完請幫推</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">推埋去立會/區會議員fb俾佢地回應</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7723e9124f3b80362f8ba73c37b04d3a89c75b7c","tid":1817904,"uid":234357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T09:15:16.000Z","msg":"831"},{"pid":"d7cbfbf55d2259ecbb18867bdf880fa2336edb17","tid":1817904,"uid":130626,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"2013ce1b04f0e0f24204df6313efc9a5abca85a9","tid":1817904,"uid":33660,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T06:19:53.000Z","msg":"同佢呢種性格嘅人拍拖應該好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T10:29:25.000Z","msg":"睇過佢啲訪問，佢個人好開朗同幽默，我諗齋同佢做朋友都會好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f387d44b939288370ab100eec96ab73208c2c1d","tid":1817904,"uid":130466,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e5b0d8e7db4def337c12eade90dffdbbd4568957","tid":1817904,"uid":51041,"like":209,"dislike":5,"score":204,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T13:15:45.000Z","msg":"真係好靚<br />\n<br />\n依家成個8婆咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T10:31:16.000Z","msg":"佢好似有長期病，keep 住食藥漲左難免有八婆feel"},{"pid":"6c809da72f26b0c32ae5c9d65d7a8dcc1207f479","tid":1817904,"uid":255964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"17940137b610133899868fbd9dc109e79d27d00e","tid":